{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm going to talk about your mindset."},{"time":4000,"text":"Does your mindset correspond to my dataset?"},{"time":8000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":9000,"text":"If not, one or the other needs upgrading, isn't it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":12000,"text":"When I talk to my students about global issues,"},{"time":16000,"text":"and I listen to them in the coffee break,"},{"time":18000,"text":"they always talk about \"we\" and \"them.\""},{"time":21000,"text":"And when they come back into the lecture room"},{"time":24000,"text":"I ask them, \"What do you mean with \"we\" and \"them\"?"},{"time":26000,"text":"\"Oh, it's very easy. It's the western world and it's the developing world,\" they say."},{"time":29000,"text":"\"We learned it in college.\""},{"time":31000,"text":"And what is the definition then? \"The definition?"},{"time":33000,"text":"Everyone knows,\" they say."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35000,"text":"But then you know, I press them like this."},{"time":37000,"text":"So one girl said, very cleverly, \"It's very easy."},{"time":39000,"text":"Western world is a long life in a small family."},{"time":42000,"text":"Developing world is a short life in a large family.\""},{"time":45000,"text":"And I like that definition, because it enabled me"},{"time":48000,"text":"to transfer their mindset"},{"time":50000,"text":"into the dataset."},{"time":52000,"text":"And here you have the dataset."},{"time":54000,"text":"So, you can see that what we have on this axis here"},{"time":56000,"text":"is size of family. One, two, three, four, five"},{"time":59000,"text":"children per woman on this axis."},{"time":61000,"text":"And here, length of life, life expectancy,"},{"time":63000,"text":"30, 40, 50."},{"time":65000,"text":"Exactly what the students said was their concept about the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69000,"text":"And really this is about the bedroom."},{"time":71000,"text":"Whether the man and woman decide to have small family,"},{"time":75000,"text":"and take care of their kids, and how long they will live."},{"time":78000,"text":"It's about the bathroom and the kitchen. If you have soap, water and food, you know,"},{"time":82000,"text":"you can live long."},{"time":84000,"text":"And the students were right. It wasn't that the world consisted --"},{"time":86000,"text":"the world consisted here, of one set of countries over here,"},{"time":90000,"text":"which had large families and short life. Developing world."},{"time":94000,"text":"And we had one set of countries up there"},{"time":97000,"text":"which was the western world."},{"time":99000,"text":"They had small families and long life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"And you are going to see here"},{"time":104000,"text":"the amazing thing that has happened in the world during my lifetime."},{"time":108000,"text":"Then the developing countries applied"},{"time":110000,"text":"soap and water, vaccination."},{"time":112000,"text":"And all the developing world started to apply family planning."},{"time":115000,"text":"And partly to USA who help to provide"},{"time":117000,"text":"technical advice and investment."},{"time":120000,"text":"And you see all the world moves over to a two child family,"},{"time":124000,"text":"and a life with 60 to 70 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"But some countries remain back in this area here."},{"time":130000,"text":"And you can see we still have Afghanistan down here."},{"time":133000,"text":"We have Liberia. We have Congo."},{"time":136000,"text":"So we have countries living there."},{"time":138000,"text":"So the problem I had"},{"time":140000,"text":"is that the worldview that my students had"},{"time":144000,"text":"corresponds to reality in the world"},{"time":146000,"text":"the year their teachers were born."},{"time":149000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":152000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":155000,"text":"And we, in fact, when we have played this over the world."},{"time":158000,"text":"I was at the Global Health Conference here in Washington last week,"},{"time":161000,"text":"and I could see the wrong concept"},{"time":164000,"text":"even active people in United States had,"},{"time":167000,"text":"that they didn't realize the improvement"},{"time":170000,"text":"of Mexico there, and China, in relation to United States."},{"time":175000,"text":"Look here when I move them forward."},{"time":177000,"text":"Here we go."},{"time":184000,"text":"They catch up. There's Mexico."},{"time":187000,"text":"It's on par with United States in these two social dimensions."},{"time":190000,"text":"There was less than five percent"},{"time":192000,"text":"of the specialists in Global Health that was aware of this."},{"time":195000,"text":"This great nation, Mexico,"},{"time":197000,"text":"has the problem that arms are coming from North,"},{"time":200000,"text":"across the borders, so they had to stop that,"},{"time":202000,"text":"because they have this strange relationship to the United States, you know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206000,"text":"But if I would change this axis here,"},{"time":210000,"text":"I would instead put income per person."},{"time":213000,"text":"Income per person. I can put that here."},{"time":216000,"text":"And we will then see"},{"time":218000,"text":"a completely different picture."},{"time":220000,"text":"By the way, I'm teaching you"},{"time":222000,"text":"how to use our website, Gapminder World,"},{"time":224000,"text":"while I'm correcting this,"},{"time":226000,"text":"because this is a free utility on the net."},{"time":229000,"text":"And when I now finally got it right,"},{"time":232000,"text":"I can go back 200 years in history."},{"time":236000,"text":"And I can find United States up there."},{"time":240000,"text":"And I can let the other countries be shown."},{"time":243000,"text":"And now I have income per person on this axis."},{"time":246000,"text":"And United States only had some, one, two thousand dollars at that time."},{"time":249000,"text":"And the life expectancy was 35 to 40 years,"},{"time":253000,"text":"on par with Afghanistan today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255000,"text":"And what has happened in the world, I will show now."},{"time":260000,"text":"This is instead of studying history"},{"time":262000,"text":"for one year at university."},{"time":264000,"text":"You can watch me for one minute now and you'll see the whole thing."},{"time":267000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":269000,"text":"You can see how the brown bubbles, which is west Europe,"},{"time":274000,"text":"and the yellow one, which is the United States,"},{"time":277000,"text":"they get richer and richer and also"},{"time":279000,"text":"start to get healthier and healthier."},{"time":281000,"text":"And this is now 100 years ago,"},{"time":283000,"text":"where the rest of the world remains behind."},{"time":286000,"text":"Here we come. And that was the influenza."},{"time":291000,"text":"That's why we are so scared about flu, isn't it?"},{"time":294000,"text":"It's still remembered. The fall of life expectancy."},{"time":297000,"text":"And then we come up. Not until"},{"time":300000,"text":"independence started."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302000,"text":"Look here You have China over there,"},{"time":304000,"text":"you have India over there,"},{"time":306000,"text":"and this is what has happened."},{"time":314000,"text":"Did you note there, that we have Mexico up there?"},{"time":317000,"text":"Mexico is not at all on par with the United States,"},{"time":319000,"text":"but they are quite close."},{"time":321000,"text":"And especially, it's interesting to see"},{"time":323000,"text":"China and the United States"},{"time":325000,"text":"during 200 years,"},{"time":328000,"text":"because I have my oldest son now working for Google,"},{"time":330000,"text":"after Google acquired this software."},{"time":333000,"text":"Because in fact, this is child labor. My son and his wife sat in a closet"},{"time":336000,"text":"for many years and developed this."},{"time":338000,"text":"And my youngest son, who studied Chinese in Beijing."},{"time":342000,"text":"So they come in with the two perspectives I have, you know?"},{"time":346000,"text":"And my son, youngest son who studied in Beijing,"},{"time":348000,"text":"in China, he got a long-term perspective."},{"time":352000,"text":"Whereas when my oldest son, who works for Google,"},{"time":354000,"text":"he should develop by quarter, or by half-year."},{"time":358000,"text":"Or Google is quite generous, so he can have one or two years to go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361000,"text":"But in China they look generation after generation"},{"time":363000,"text":"because they remember"},{"time":366000,"text":"the very embarrassing period, for 100 years,"},{"time":368000,"text":"when they went backwards."},{"time":370000,"text":"And then they would remember the first part"},{"time":373000,"text":"of last century, which was really bad,"},{"time":376000,"text":"and we could go by this so-called Great Leap Forward."},{"time":379000,"text":"But this was 1963."},{"time":381000,"text":"Mao Tse-Tung eventually brought health to China,"},{"time":385000,"text":"and then he died, and then Deng Xiaoping started"},{"time":387000,"text":"this amazing move forward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":389000,"text":"Isn't it strange to see that the United States"},{"time":391000,"text":"first grew the economy, and then gradually got rich?"},{"time":395000,"text":"Whereas China could get healthy much earlier,"},{"time":398000,"text":"because they applied the knowledge of education, nutrition,"},{"time":402000,"text":"and then also benefits of penicillin"},{"time":405000,"text":"and vaccines and family planning."},{"time":407000,"text":"And Asia could have social development"},{"time":410000,"text":"before they got the economic development."},{"time":413000,"text":"So to me, as a public health professor,"},{"time":415000,"text":"it's not strange that all these countries grow so fast now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":419000,"text":"Because what you see here, what you see here"},{"time":421000,"text":"is the flat world of Thomas Friedman,"},{"time":424000,"text":"isn't it."},{"time":426000,"text":"It's not really, really flat."},{"time":428000,"text":"But the middle income countries --"},{"time":430000,"text":"and this is where I suggest to my students,"},{"time":432000,"text":"stop using the concept \"developing world.\""},{"time":435000,"text":"Because after all, talking about the developing world"},{"time":438000,"text":"is like having two chapters in the history of the United States."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442000,"text":"The last chapter is about present, and president Obama,"},{"time":446000,"text":"and the other is about the past,"},{"time":448000,"text":"where you cover everything from Washington"},{"time":450000,"text":"to Eisenhower."},{"time":452000,"text":"Because Washington to Eisenhower,"},{"time":454000,"text":"that is what we find in the developing world."},{"time":456000,"text":"We could actually go to Mayflower"},{"time":458000,"text":"to Eisenhower,"},{"time":460000,"text":"and that would be put together into a developing world,"},{"time":463000,"text":"which is rightly growing its cities in a very amazing way,"},{"time":466000,"text":"which have great entrepreneurs,"},{"time":468000,"text":"but also have the collapsing countries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":471000,"text":"So, how could we make better sense about this?"},{"time":474000,"text":"Well, one way of trying is to see whether we could"},{"time":477000,"text":"look at income distribution."},{"time":479000,"text":"This is the income distribution of peoples in the world,"},{"time":482000,"text":"from $1. This is where you have food to eat."},{"time":485000,"text":"These people go to bed hungry."},{"time":487000,"text":"And this is the number of people."},{"time":489000,"text":"This is $10, whether you have a public or a private"},{"time":491000,"text":"health service system. This is where you can"},{"time":493000,"text":"provide health service for your family and school for your children,"},{"time":496000,"text":"and this is OECD countries:"},{"time":498000,"text":"Green, Latin America, East Europe."},{"time":500000,"text":"This is East Asia, and the light blue there is South Asia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":504000,"text":"And this is how the world changed."},{"time":507000,"text":"It changed like this."},{"time":509000,"text":"Can you see how it's growing? And how hundreds of millions"},{"time":512000,"text":"and billions is coming out of poverty in Asia?"},{"time":515000,"text":"And it goes over here?"},{"time":517000,"text":"And I come now, into projections,"},{"time":519000,"text":"but I have to stop at the door of Lehman Brothers there, you know, because --"},{"time":522000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":525000,"text":"that's where the projections are not valid any longer."},{"time":527000,"text":"Probably the world will do this."},{"time":529000,"text":"and then it will continue forward like this."},{"time":532000,"text":"But more or less, this is what will happen,"},{"time":534000,"text":"and we have a world which cannot be looked upon as divided."}]},{"cues":[{"time":539000,"text":"We have the high income countries here,"},{"time":541000,"text":"with the United States as a leading power;"},{"time":544000,"text":"we have the emerging economies in the middle,"},{"time":547000,"text":"which provide a lot of the funding for the bailout;"},{"time":549000,"text":"and we have the low income countries here."},{"time":552000,"text":"Yeah, this is a fact that from where the money comes,"},{"time":555000,"text":"they have been saving, you know, over the last decade."},{"time":557000,"text":"And here we have the low income countries"},{"time":559000,"text":"where entrepreneurs are."},{"time":561000,"text":"And here we have the countries in collapse and war,"},{"time":564000,"text":"like Afghanistan, Somalia, parts of Congo, Darfur."},{"time":569000,"text":"We have all this at the same time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":571000,"text":"That's why it's so problematic to describe what has happened"},{"time":573000,"text":"in the developing world."},{"time":575000,"text":"Because it's so different, what has happened there."},{"time":577000,"text":"And that's why I suggest"},{"time":579000,"text":"a slightly different approach of what you would call it."},{"time":582000,"text":"And you have huge differences within countries also."},{"time":586000,"text":"I heard that your departments here were by regions."},{"time":589000,"text":"Here you have Sub-Saharan Africa, South Asia,"},{"time":592000,"text":"East Asia, Arab states,"},{"time":594000,"text":"East Europe, Latin America, and OECD."},{"time":596000,"text":"And on this axis, GDP."},{"time":598000,"text":"And on this, heath, child survival,"},{"time":600000,"text":"and it doesn't come as a surprise"},{"time":602000,"text":"that Africa south of Sahara is at the bottom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605000,"text":"But when I split it, when I split it"},{"time":607000,"text":"into country bubbles,"},{"time":609000,"text":"the size of the bubbles here is the population."},{"time":612000,"text":"Then you see Sierra Leone and Mauritius, completely different."},{"time":615000,"text":"There is such a difference within Sub-Saharan Africa."},{"time":617000,"text":"And I can split the others. Here is the South Asian,"},{"time":620000,"text":"Arab world."},{"time":622000,"text":"Now all your different departments."},{"time":624000,"text":"East Europe, Latin America, and OECD countries."},{"time":627000,"text":"And here were are. We have a continuum in the world."},{"time":630000,"text":"We cannot put it into two parts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":632000,"text":"It is Mayflower down here. It is Washington here,"},{"time":635000,"text":"building, building countries."},{"time":637000,"text":"It's Lincoln here, advancing them."},{"time":641000,"text":"It's Eisenhower bringing modernity into the countries."},{"time":644000,"text":"And then it's United States today, up here."},{"time":646000,"text":"And we have countries all this way."},{"time":648000,"text":"Now, this is the important thing"},{"time":651000,"text":"of understanding how the world has changed."},{"time":655000,"text":"At this point I decided to make a pause."},{"time":659000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":661000,"text":"And it is my task, on behalf of the rest of the world,"},{"time":664000,"text":"to convey a thanks to the U.S. taxpayers,"},{"time":668000,"text":"for Demographic Health Survey."},{"time":670000,"text":"Many are not aware of -- no, this is not a joke."},{"time":673000,"text":"This is very serious."},{"time":675000,"text":"It is due to USA's continuous sponsoring"},{"time":679000,"text":"during 25 years of the very good methodology"},{"time":682000,"text":"for measuring child mortality"},{"time":684000,"text":"that we have a grasp of what's happening in the world."},{"time":687000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":694000,"text":"And it is U.S. government at its best,"},{"time":697000,"text":"without advocacy, providing facts,"},{"time":700000,"text":"that it's useful for the society."},{"time":702000,"text":"And providing data free of charge"},{"time":705000,"text":"on the internet, for the world to use. Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":708000,"text":"Quite the opposite of the World Bank,"},{"time":710000,"text":"who compiled data with government money,"},{"time":713000,"text":"tax money, and then they sell it to add a little profit,"},{"time":716000,"text":"in a very inefficient, Gutenberg way."},{"time":719000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":725000,"text":"But the people doing that at the World Bank"},{"time":727000,"text":"are among the best in the world."},{"time":729000,"text":"And they are highly skilled professionals."},{"time":731000,"text":"It's just that we would like to upgrade our international agencies"},{"time":735000,"text":"to deal with the world in the modern way, as we do."},{"time":738000,"text":"And when it comes to free data and transparency,"},{"time":741000,"text":"United States of America is one of the best."},{"time":744000,"text":"And that doesn't come easy from the mouth of a Swedish public health professor."},{"time":747000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":750000,"text":"And I'm not paid to come here, no."}]},{"cues":[{"time":753000,"text":"I would like to show you what happens with the data,"},{"time":755000,"text":"what we can show with this data."},{"time":757000,"text":"Look here. This is the world."},{"time":759000,"text":"With income down there and child mortality."},{"time":761000,"text":"And what has happened in the world?"},{"time":763000,"text":"Since 1950, during the last 50 years"},{"time":766000,"text":"we have had a fall in child mortality."},{"time":769000,"text":"And it is the DHS that makes it possible to know this."},{"time":771000,"text":"And we had an increase in income."},{"time":773000,"text":"And the blue former developing countries"},{"time":775000,"text":"are mixing up with the former industrialized western world."},{"time":780000,"text":"We have a continuum. But we still have, of course,"},{"time":783000,"text":"Congo, up there. We still have as poor countries"},{"time":786000,"text":"as we have had, always, in history."},{"time":790000,"text":"And that's the bottom billion, where we've heard today"},{"time":793000,"text":"about a completely new approach to do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":796000,"text":"And how fast has this happened?"},{"time":799000,"text":"Well, MDG 4."},{"time":801000,"text":"The United States has not been so eager"},{"time":803000,"text":"to use MDG 4."},{"time":806000,"text":"But you have been the main sponsor that has enabled us to measure it,"},{"time":809000,"text":"because it's the only child mortality that we can measure."},{"time":812000,"text":"And we used to say that it should fall four percent per year."},{"time":815000,"text":"Let's see what Sweden has done."},{"time":817000,"text":"We used to boast about fast social progress."},{"time":820000,"text":"That's where we were, 1900."},{"time":822000,"text":"1900, Sweden was there."},{"time":824000,"text":"Same child mortality as Bangladesh had, 1990,"},{"time":826000,"text":"though they had lower income."},{"time":828000,"text":"They started very well. They used the aid well."},{"time":831000,"text":"They vaccinated the kids. They get better water."},{"time":833000,"text":"And they reduced child mortality,"},{"time":835000,"text":"with an amazing 4.7 percent per year. They beat Sweden."},{"time":838000,"text":"I run Sweden the same 16 year period."}]},{"cues":[{"time":842000,"text":"Second round, it's Sweden, 1916,"},{"time":844000,"text":"against Egypt, 1990."},{"time":846000,"text":"Here we go. Once again the USA is part of the reason here."},{"time":849000,"text":"They get safe water, they get food for the poor,"},{"time":853000,"text":"and they get malaria eradicated."},{"time":855000,"text":"5.5 percent. They are faster than the millennium development goal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":858000,"text":"And third chance for Sweden, against Brazil here."},{"time":861000,"text":"Brazil here has amazing social improvement"},{"time":865000,"text":"over the last 16 years,"},{"time":867000,"text":"and they go faster than Sweden."},{"time":869000,"text":"This means that the world is converging."},{"time":871000,"text":"The middle income countries,"},{"time":873000,"text":"the emerging economy, they are catching up."},{"time":875000,"text":"They are moving to cities,"},{"time":877000,"text":"where they also get better assistance for that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":879000,"text":"Well the Swedish students protest at this point."},{"time":882000,"text":"They say, \"This is not fair,"},{"time":884000,"text":"because these countries had vaccines and antibiotics"},{"time":886000,"text":"that were not available for Sweden."},{"time":888000,"text":"We have to do real-time competition.\""},{"time":890000,"text":"Okay. I give you Singapore, the year I was born."},{"time":893000,"text":"Singapore had twice the child mortality of Sweden."},{"time":895000,"text":"It's the most tropical country in the world,"},{"time":897000,"text":"a marshland on the equator."},{"time":899000,"text":"And here we go. It took a little time for them to get independent."},{"time":902000,"text":"But then they started to grow their economy."},{"time":904000,"text":"And they made the social investment. They got away malaria."},{"time":906000,"text":"They got a magnificent health system"},{"time":908000,"text":"that beat both the U.S. and Sweden."},{"time":910000,"text":"We never thought it would happen that they would win over Sweden!"},{"time":913000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":921000,"text":"All these green countries are achieving millennium development goals."},{"time":924000,"text":"These yellow are just about to be doing this."},{"time":926000,"text":"These red are the countries that doesn't do it, and the policy has to be improved."},{"time":929000,"text":"Not simplistic extrapolation."},{"time":932000,"text":"We have to really find a way"},{"time":934000,"text":"of supporting those countries in a better way."},{"time":936000,"text":"We have to respect the middle income countries"},{"time":939000,"text":"on what they are doing."},{"time":941000,"text":"And we have to fact-base the whole way we look at the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":944000,"text":"This is dollar per person. This is HIV in the countries."},{"time":947000,"text":"The blue is Africa."},{"time":949000,"text":"The size of the bubbles is how many are HIV affected."},{"time":952000,"text":"You see the tragedy in South Africa there."},{"time":954000,"text":"About 20 percent of the adult population are infected."},{"time":957000,"text":"And in spite of them having quite a high income,"},{"time":960000,"text":"they have a huge number of HIV infected."},{"time":963000,"text":"But you also see that there are African countries down here."},{"time":966000,"text":"There is no such thing as an HIV epidemic in Africa."},{"time":970000,"text":"There's a number, five to 10 countries in Africa"},{"time":973000,"text":"that has the same level as Sweden and United States."},{"time":976000,"text":"And there are others who are extremely high."}]},{"cues":[{"time":978000,"text":"And I will show you that what has happened"},{"time":981000,"text":"in one of the best countries, with the most vibrant economy"},{"time":985000,"text":"in Africa and a good governance, Botswana."},{"time":988000,"text":"They have a very high level. It's coming down."},{"time":990000,"text":"But now it's not falling,"},{"time":992000,"text":"because there, with help from PEPFAR,"},{"time":994000,"text":"it's working with treatment. And people are not dying."},{"time":997000,"text":"And you can see it's not that easy,"},{"time":1000000,"text":"that it is war which caused this."},{"time":1003000,"text":"Because here, in Congo, there is war."},{"time":1005000,"text":"And here, in Zambia, there is peace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1008000,"text":"And it's not the economy. Richer country has a little higher."},{"time":1011000,"text":"If I split Tanzania in its income,"},{"time":1013000,"text":"the richer 20 percent in Tanzania"},{"time":1015000,"text":"has more HIV than the poorest one."},{"time":1017000,"text":"And it's really different within each country."},{"time":1020000,"text":"Look at the provinces of Kenya. They are very different."},{"time":1022000,"text":"And this is the situation you see."},{"time":1025000,"text":"It's not deep poverty. It's the special situation,"},{"time":1028000,"text":"probably of concurrent sexual partnership"},{"time":1031000,"text":"among part of the heterosexual population"},{"time":1034000,"text":"in some countries, or some parts of countries,"},{"time":1036000,"text":"in south and eastern Africa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1038000,"text":"Don't make it Africa. Don't make it a race issue."},{"time":1041000,"text":"Make it a local issue. And do prevention at each place,"},{"time":1045000,"text":"in the way it can be done there."},{"time":1047000,"text":"So to just end up,"},{"time":1050000,"text":"there are things of suffering"},{"time":1053000,"text":"in the one billion poorest, which we don't know."},{"time":1056000,"text":"Those who live beyond the cellphone,"},{"time":1058000,"text":"those who have yet to see a computer,"},{"time":1060000,"text":"those who have no electricity at home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1063000,"text":"This is the disease, Konzo, I spent 20 years"},{"time":1065000,"text":"elucidating in Africa."},{"time":1067000,"text":"It's caused by fast processing of toxic cassava root in famine situation."},{"time":1072000,"text":"It's similar to the pellagra epidemic in Mississippi in the '30s."},{"time":1076000,"text":"It's similar to other nutritional diseases."},{"time":1079000,"text":"It will never affect a rich person."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1081000,"text":"We have seen it here in Mozambique."},{"time":1084000,"text":"This is the epidemic in Mozambique. This is an epidemic in northern Tanzania."},{"time":1087000,"text":"You never heard about the disease."},{"time":1089000,"text":"But it's much more than Ebola"},{"time":1091000,"text":"that has been affected by this disease."},{"time":1093000,"text":"Cause crippling throughout the world."},{"time":1095000,"text":"And over the last two years,"},{"time":1097000,"text":"2,000 people has been crippled"},{"time":1099000,"text":"in the southern tip of Bandundu region."},{"time":1101000,"text":"That used to be the illegal diamond trade,"},{"time":1103000,"text":"from the UNITA-dominated area in Angola."},{"time":1106000,"text":"That has now disappeared,"},{"time":1108000,"text":"and they are now in great economic problem."},{"time":1110000,"text":"And one week ago, for the first time,"},{"time":1113000,"text":"there were four lines on the Internet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1116000,"text":"Don't get confused of the progress of the emerging economies"},{"time":1119000,"text":"and the great capacity"},{"time":1122000,"text":"of people in the middle income countries"},{"time":1124000,"text":"and in peaceful low income countries."},{"time":1126000,"text":"There is still mystery in one billion."},{"time":1128000,"text":"And we have to have more concepts"},{"time":1130000,"text":"than just developing countries and developing world."},{"time":1133000,"text":"We need a new mindset. The world is converging,"},{"time":1136000,"text":"but -- but -- but not the bottom billion."},{"time":1139000,"text":"They are still as poor as they've ever been."},{"time":1142000,"text":"It's not sustainable, and it will not happen around one superpower."},{"time":1147000,"text":"But you will remain"},{"time":1149000,"text":"one of the most important superpowers,"},{"time":1152000,"text":"and the most hopeful superpower, for the time to be."},{"time":1155000,"text":"And this institution"},{"time":1157000,"text":"will have a very crucial role,"},{"time":1159000,"text":"not for United States, but for the world."},{"time":1161000,"text":"So you have a very bad name,"},{"time":1164000,"text":"State Department. This is not the State Department."},{"time":1166000,"text":"It's the World Department."},{"time":1168000,"text":"And we have a high hope in you. Thank you very much."},{"time":1170000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}